{"tid":1629853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭唔肯撤回612暴動定義嘅原因","createTime":"2019-10-06T10:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T10:46:21.000Z","uid":319231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05c65c5301b8f41247c3470d481591a81669b438","tid":1629853,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:42:30.000Z","msg":"林鄭一開始標籤左和平示威者做「暴徒」，係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">別有用心</span></strong>！！！<br />\n<br />\n最近聽聞有個理論「labelling theory」：<br />\n<br />\n社會上有權有勢嘅人，為左鞏固自己利益，會利用「標籤」，剝削及抑壓威脅到佢哋嘅人<br />\n<br />\n「標籤」後，慢慢，社會上其他人只會睇到佢哋負面嘅「標籤」 。被標籤嘅人做咩都無用，就進一步做違規行為，結果應驗左當初嘅「標籤」同偏見<br />\n<br />\n例子：以前白人會label黑人「懶惰」，打擊佢哋就業機會，結果佢哋就真係搵唔到工，人們就覺得佢哋真係懶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當社會上嘅人覺得和平示威者只係「暴徒」&mdash;-&gt; <br />\nwe have no stake in the society ，可以唔聽示威者訴求 &mdash;-&gt;<br />\n示威者只好將行動升級 &mdash;-&gt;<br />\n然後就跌入陷阱，因為示威者已經應驗左「暴徒」嘅label<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我哋要走出呢個陷阱</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要反思，諗吓而定做緊嘅事，社會上各界人士甚至國際上會點睇我哋<br />\n<br />\n從來都只有暴政 沒有暴徒<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"34112e28b817237a94666a9becd03b1e3308b185","tid":1629853,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:42:48.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"3f19b76207c0bf0a1a353e7cdb7c345eb7a5fe92","tid":1629853,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:43:02.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"548b2a294ce60b7f88138aca57f7b1136c843187","tid":1629853,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"人"},{"pid":"7e1a435d24df358d80d970935a55d864b4da2352","tid":1629853,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:43:22.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj